snippet.title: Scooby-doo 2: Monsters Unleashed Trailer
snippet.description: Scooby and the gang confront an anonymous masked villain who is plotting to take over the city of Coolsville by wreaking mayhem with a monster machine that creates Mystery Inc.'s classic foes.
